title: [Proposal] Distribute 2110 LPOP tokens for community engagement rewards
body:
HaloDAO (HALO) has seen strong user adoption from its inception to its launching. The team is rewarding community participation with LPOP tokens.

In line with this, the team will be distributing 2110 LPOP tokens on July 5, 2021.
